            <lg xml:id="TK1101">
<l>kaṇṭukēṭ ṭuṇṭuyirt tuṟṟaṟiyu maimpulaṉu</l>
<l>moṇṭoṭi kaṇṇē yuḷa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The (simultaneous) enjoyment of the five senses of sight, hearing, taste, smell and touch can only be found with bright braceleted (women).</l>
            </lg>
